UX/UI and Development for Web & Mobile Apps

Take your product to the next level of customer experience

Hire Top 5% Designers

UX/UI services

Assistance

Web design

We create and launch outstanding websites for your products, or services.

Product design

Our team creates efficient mobile app design with clear product interface structure and awesome UI style.

Cross-platform experiences design

We provide multi-platform UI/UX design that perfectly works on different devices

Our team

50 +
Team members
  • UI/UX designers
  • Developers
  • QA Engineers
  • Business Analysts
  • Project Managers
  • Management
Hire us

Cases

We bring real solutions to each client’s problems through a deep understanding of their market, solution, and vision.

See all cases

Read More
The Snotor (formerly MassMedia) team has a great attitude. When you work with them, you feel you’re the center of their attention.

Why choose us?

Advantages

Business approach to development

Advanced 16 years Expertise

Lifetime Code Warranty

Enhanced business value of products

More services

Solution Development

We will be happy to assist you at any and every stage of the software development lifecycle: from conceptualization, business analysis and prototyping to the development and deployment of a complete solution

Offshore development center

We can help you save up to 60% of your software development project execution expenses. Get your ideal development team with experienced management to make your project perfect

PoC for Sturtups

With our executive team members helping to launch and restart a number of companies in the last 10 years, we know the value of technology and what good Proof of Concept can do to change the opinion of the potential investors. That’s why we came up with a special offering for companies that want to quickly and relatively inexpensively test out new ideas.
